72
73 // Tests are reversed to catch NaNs.
74 if (!(x < 8.f))
75 return 1.f;
76 if (!(x > -8.f))
77 return -1.f;
78 float sign = 1.f;
79 if (x < 0.f) {
80 x = -x;
81 sign = -1.f;
82 }
83 // Look-up.
84 int i = static_cast<int>(std::floor(0.5f + 25 * x));
85 float y = kTansigTable[i];
86 // Map i back to x's scale (undo 25 factor).
87 x -= 0.04f * i;
88 y = y + x * (1.f - y * y) * (1.f - y * x);
89 return sign * y;
90}
91
92inline float SigmoidApproximated(const float x) {
93 return 0.5f + 0.5f * TansigApproximated(0.5f * x);
94}
95
96inline float RectifiedLinearUnit(const float x) {
97 return x < 0.f ? 0.f : x;
98}
